data.description: This home is almost ready for a family and a fantastic option for a long-term investor. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, with a half bath located on the first floor, the upstairs is remodeled with two full bathrooms and large bedrooms, and a catwalk overlooking the great rooms for family get-togethers. Close to shopping, parks, great Elk Grove schools, and freeway access, it comes with all appliances, including washer and dryer, refrigerator, stove and dishwasher. All other furniture is negotiable in the sale.
